description:
Watch as the story of the abduction of Dinah, Jacob’s daughter, from Genesis Chapter 34 and Genesis Chapter 35 comes to life in iBIBLE—the world’s first visual and interactive Bible. Featured in the twenty-third chapter of iBIBLE is the story of Dinah, Jacob’s daughter, who was taken by Shechem, a local ruler’s son, and forced himself on her. The sons of Jacob devised a plan and answered Shechem deceitfully when he asked for Dinah to be his wife. After all the men of Shechem’s city were circumcised, Levi and Simeon descended on the city. Study the Bible with your kids and enjoy the narrative presentation of God’s Word with iBIBLE.

A production of RevelationMedia, iBIBLE brings God’s Word to life in a format that people all over the world can engage with. Through dramatic audio and vibrant animation, people of all ages, all backgrounds, and with all abilities can learn the Biblical narrative—the one cohesive story of Scripture. iBIBLE will be available for free to translate into any of the world’s 7,000+ languages. Join the movement today and help bring the true story of God’s Word to the nations for free!

www.i.BIBLE

Director: Steve Cleary
